<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <% include ../partials/head %>
</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <% include ../partials/header %>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
        <div class="row mt-3" style="align-content: center; text-align: center">
            <div class="col">
                <h2><%= release_name %></h2>
                <h3><%= release_artist %></h3>
                <img src="<%= release_artwork %>" class="img-thumbnail art" alt="coverart" height="25%" width="25%" />
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mt-3">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="row">
                    <h5 class="col-md-7 ml-5 text-left">
                        Release Type:
                    </h5>
                    <h5 class="col text-left">
                        <%= release_type %>
                    </h5>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <h5 class="col-md-7 ml-5 text-left">
                        Release Date:
                    </h5>
                    <h5 class="col text-left">
                        <%= release_date %>
                    </h5>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <h5 class="col-md-7 ml-5 text-left">
                        Length:
                    </h5>
                    <h5 class="col text-left">
                        <%= release_length %>
                    </h5>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <h5 class="col-md-7 ml-5 text-left">
                        Label:
                    </h5>
                    <h5 class="col text-left">
                        <%= release_label %>
                    </h5>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <h5 class="col-md-7 ml-5 text-left">
                        Format(s):
                    </h5>
                    <h5 class="col text-left">
                        <%= release_formats %>
                    </h5>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <h5 class="col-md-7 ml-5 text-left">
                        Genre:
                    </h5>
                    <h5 class="col text-left">
                        <%= release_genres %>
                    </h5>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <h5 class="col-md-7 ml-5 text-left">
                        User Rating:
                    </h5>
                    <h5 class="col text-left">
                        <%= release_rating %> / 5.0
                    </h5>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="col-md-6">
                <%= release_desc %>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="row ml-5 mt-3">

        </div>

        <div id="accordion" class="ml-5">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header" id="headingOne">
                    <h5 class="mb-0">
                        <button class="col btn btn-link collapsed text-left text-dark" data-toggle="collapse"
                            data-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                            <h4>Tracklist</h4>
                        </button>
                    </h5>
                </div>

                <div id="collapseOne" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-parent="#accordion">
                    <div class="card-body">

                        <% tracks.forEach(function(track) { %>
                        <div class="row ml-5">
                            <h5 class="col-md-2 text-center">
                                <%= track.number %>
                            </h5>
                            <h5 class="col-md-6 text-left">
                                <%= track.name %>
                            </h5>
                            <h5 class="col-md-2 text-right">
                                <%= track.length %>
                            </h5>
                            <div class="col-md-2"></div>
                        </div>
                        <% }); %>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header" id="headingTwo">
                    <h5 class="mb-0">
                        <button class="col btn btn-link collapsed text-left text-dark" data-toggle="collapse"
                            data-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                            <h4>Shopping</h4>
                        </button>
                    </h5>
                </div>
                <div id="collapseTwo" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#accordion">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <table class="table">
                            <thead class="thead-light">
                                <tr>
                                    <th scope="col">Catalogue Number</th>
                                    <th scope="col">Release Type</th>
                                    <th scope="col">Price</th>
                                    <th scope="col"></th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody>
                                <% items.forEach(function(item) { %>
                                <tr>
                                    <th scope="row"><%= item.catalog %> </th>
                                    <td><%= item.format %></td>
                                    <td>Â£<%= item.price %></td>
                                    <td class="">
                                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-success btn-sm ml-5" role="button">
                                            <img class="align-middle" style="height: 18px; width: 18px;"
                                                src="/images/shopping-cart.svg" />
                                            Add to Cart
                                        </a>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <% }); %>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header" id="headingThree">
                    <h5 class="mb-0">
                        <button class="col btn btn-link collapsed text-left text-dark" data-toggle="collapse"
                            data-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                            <h4>Reviews</h4>
                        </button>
                    </h5>
                </div>
                <div id="collapseThree" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-parent="#accordion">
                    <div class="card-body">

                        <% comments.forEach(function(comment) { %>
                        <div class="panel panel-default mt-3">
                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                <strong><%= comment.username %></strong>
                                <% for (var i = 0; i < comment.rating; i++) { %>
                                <span class=""><img src="images/star-checked.svg" /></span>
                                <% } %>
                                <% for (var i = 0; i < (5 - comment.rating); i++) { %>
                                <span class=""><img src="images/star.svg" /></span>
                                <% } %>
                                <span class="text-muted ml-2"><%= comment.date %> </span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                <%= comment.desc %>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <% }); %>
                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                <strong>Hakita</strong>
                                <span class="ml-2"><img src="images/star-checked.svg" /></span>
                                <span class=""><img src="images/star-checked.svg" /></span>
                                <span class=""><img src="images/star-checked.svg" /></span>
                                <span class=""><img src="images/star-checked.svg" /></span>
                                <span class=""><img src="images/star.svg" /></span>
                                <span class="text-muted ml-2">09.02.2019</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                The variety on display here is great. A lot of the songs are meh but since they're all
                                pretty short it won't take long until you're on something new and fresh.
                                The post-rock and ambient tracks were by far my favorite, such as Slum and Backtrack
                                Observation, though a lot of banger tracks like How Is That Legal and Press and Turn
                                were great too.
                                The only real downsides of this album are the fact that, since it's 38 songs, you're
                                bound to not even remember half of them by the time you're done and a couple awkward
                                moments of attempts at comedy.
                                Regardless, it's a good album with lots of relisten value and charm.

                                It's the kinda album that's easy to just put on and let flow, making it pretty
                                accessible.
                                Despite being long, I was never once bored during it, and will probably relisten to it
                                in the future.

                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="panel panel-default mt-3">
                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                <strong>1Chops</strong>
                                <span class="ml-2"><img src="images/star-checked.svg" /></span>
                                <span class=""><img src="images/star-checked.svg" /></span>
                                <span class=""><img src="images/star-checked.svg" /></span>
                                <span class=""><img src="images/star.svg" /></span>
                                <span class=""><img src="images/star.svg" /></span>
                                <span class="text-muted ml-2">01.01.2018 </span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                Haven't heard the whole thing yet, but if the batting average keeps up over the whole
                                project, this is the first really good album of 2o18. It's so rare that I can get
                                excited about instrumental rock, but the atmosphere Naked Flames created is so dead-on
                                perfect that I can't help but get drawn in. Defo feels like some kinda dream diary.

                                I guess my only real complaint is that some of the longer songs get kinda meandery/lose
                                me a little as they stretch onward ("Secretweapon" really does this in that first half).
                                And the absence of a human voice really goes noticed sometimes. Other than that THESE
                                TUNES ARE GOOD and I'm excited to finish off the tracklist.

                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="jumbotron mt-3 pt-3 pb-2 pl-4 pr-4 border">
                            <form>
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="user_comment">Post your own comment:</label>
                                    <span class="ml-2"><img src="images/star-checked.svg" /></span>
                                    <span class=""><img src="images/star-checked.svg" /></span>
                                    <span class=""><img src="images/star-checked.svg" /></span>
                                    <span class=""><img src="images/star.svg" /></span>
                                    <span class=""><img src="images/star.svg" /></span>
                                    <textarea class="form-control" id="user_comment" rows="5"></textarea>
                                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark mt-2">Post Comment</button>
                                </div>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </main>

    <footer>
        <% include ../partials/footer %>
    </footer>

</body>

</html>